-- `ids`, matching `org_id` and `app_id`, with optional `machine_id` narrowing.
-- `ids_and_names`, matching `org_id`, `app_id`, `org_name`, and `app_name`, with optional `machine_id` and `machine_name` narrowing.
-- `names`, matching `org_name` and `app_name`, with optional `machine_name` narrowing. This mode exists only for compatibility; immutable IDs or IDs-and-names are preferred.
